{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/Collect_mushrooms.gif?t=1740243923\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a break from the hustle and bustle of the city by walking through a picturesque forest. Enjoy nature, pick mushrooms and immerse yourself in the atmosphere of tranquility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forest paths hide many secrets. Explore every corner, find rare species of mushrooms and become a true connoisseur of mycology!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/2.gif?t=1740243923\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore seven different locations with their unique places and vegetation, varied weather and mushroom picking conditions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features 32 popular types of mushrooms with their own growing areas. Each mushroom has several stages of growth, its own unique quality level and weight.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete various tasks, participate in festivals and mushroom picking competitions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your basket and knife to collect more mushrooms and get more experience and coins.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3262810?t=1740243923","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3262810?t=1740243923","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/c0d26aae91da1e8945ab21f2c74281c1d4fedd8b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740243923","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/c0d26aae91da1e8945ab21f2c74281c1d